<br>
What are the general feelings about playing alts who are not in BotL guild? For example, ive struggled to get any further with silentjay and ive lost interest in the quests i was doing simpley because they are dangerous. <br>
<br>
I decided to play my druid who is in a different guild, but i feel very guilty about it as BotL is my &quot;family guild&quot;. My main reason for playing druid is for diversity and to get money. Silent and others have a serious lack if money. (as im sure your chars are too)<br>
<br>
